data.description: This is a well maintained home with 8.42 acres of land.  There is level land around the house and hill woodland behind the house.  This property is near Manchester, Kentucky (about 3 miles west) and is an excellent location for anyone that works in Manchester or London, Kentucky.  The property has all public facilities.  There is ample acreage for more site built or manufactured homes.  If you want something nice to be proud of in an excellent location and scenic area, you will surely like this property.  Call listing agent John Sandlin 606-598-3967.
